<h2 id="provenance">Provenance</h2>
<h3 id="winery">Winery</h3>
<p>Inaugural vintage of Sauvignon Blanc was in 1982, a bordeaux / sauvignon blanc blend</p>
<ul>
  <li>Winery founded by Dan and Margaret Duckhorn in 1976
    <ul>
      <li>one of the first 40 Napa Valley wineries</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Dedicated to making classic wines that reflect the unique character and quality of the vineyards</li>
</ul>

